==Trivia==
[[File:Three-headed Gryphon in Collection Log.png|thumb|right|The shellbane gryphon's [[collection log]] tab in the [[August 2025 Sailing Stress Test]], then called the Three-headed Gryphon.]]
* The shellbane gryphon is the second boss that players may have to kill as part of an elite clue step, the first being the [[King Black Dragon]].
** It is also the second Slayer boss that can be killed off-task, the first being the [[thermonuclear smoke devil]] due to being required for the Elite [[Western Provinces Diary]]. While the thermonuclear smoke devil can only be killed off-task once, the shellbane gryphon can be killed every time the corresponding clue step is rolled. This makes it possible, though very unlikely, to fully obtain its [[collection log]] without ever getting a gryphon or shellbane gryphon boss task.
* The head of the shellbane gryphon is modeled after the {{WP|Bearded vulture}}.
* The shellbane gryphon was referred to as the '''Three-headed Gryphon''' during the [[March 2025 Sailing Alpha|Sailing alpha]], [[June 2025 Sailing Beta|beta]], and [[August 2025 Sailing Stress Test|stress test]].
* The shellbane gryphon had a festive override wearing a [[santa hat]] during the [[2025 Christmas event/Gallery|2025]] Christmas event.

